title: Xyron Creative Station Home Refill, 9” x 40', Permanent Adhesive Refill-Cartridge for Label Maker, Laminator Machine, Scrapbooking Supplies, Home Office & Home School Craft Supplies (AT905-40)
description: The Xyron 9” Creative Station Home Permanent Refill cartridge is 40' long and fits into a Xyron 9” Creative Station Home. Enjoy applying edge-to-edge acid-free permanent adhesive to almost any item up to 9" wide. Great for scrapbooking, die cuts craft projects and school projects. Also fits the Xyron 900 and XRN900.
